
Text::LineEditor 

This module implements a -very- simple editor like Berkley mail used
to use.  Remember that?


INSTALLING
==========

After unzipping and untarring the distribution directory, you install
the module by running these commands:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


